Subject: [PATCH] mac80211: fix potential double free on mesh join
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4a2d4496e15ea5bb5c8e83b94ca8ca7fb045e7d3
